data.description: Impressive end unit town home/condo with NO fees located on a cul-de-sac. This home has so much to offer! Open floor plan with big open foyer and stairs with a surprise spot for decor. Renovated kitchen features a breakfast bar plus recessed lighting, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, soft close cabinets, and a sizable pantry! Large open living area includes plenty of light, cozy gas fireplace, access to back yard with patio and privacy fence, great for entertaining. Bedrooms are spacious and bright. Master bedroom’s arch shaped window, double closets and vaulted ceilings are beautiful. Only minutes from bases, beaches, marinas and shopping. No flood insurance required.
